code: @Override protected ExtendedStatsBucketPipelineAggregationBuilder buildFactory(String pipelineAggregatorName, String bucketsPath, Map<String, Object> params) {     ExtendedStatsBucketPipelineAggregationBuilder factory = new ExtendedStatsBucketPipelineAggregationBuilder(pipelineAggregatorName, bucketsPath).     Double sigma = (Double) params.get(SIGMA.getPreferredName()).     if (sigma != null) {         factory.sigma(sigma).     }     return factory. }

@Override protected boolean token(XContentParser parser, String field, XContentParser.Token token, Map<String, Object> params) throws IOException {     if (SIGMA.match(field, parser.getDeprecationHandler()) && token == XContentParser.Token.VALUE_NUMBER) {         params.put(SIGMA.getPreferredName(), parser.doubleValue()).         return true.     }     return false. }
